{"id":395121,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/【网络民议】艾未未欺世盗名-设计谋害顾城、海子/","date":"2015-06-10T06:28:05Z","modified":"2015-06-10T06:28:05Z","title":"【网络民议】艾未未欺世盗名 设计谋害顾城、海子","content":"<p><strong>新闻背景：</strong>因出演《霍比特人》三部曲中“精灵王”一角而备受中国观众喜爱的李·佩斯近日来到中国。6月7日下午，李·佩斯在刚开不久的新浪微博主页上传了一张与艾未未的合影。照片中，李佩斯嘟嘴卖萌，并称自己是艾的“死忠粉”，而艾未未则没有太多表情，微博一出旋即引来网友热议。（观察者网）</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608183707671.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-395131\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608183707671.png\" alt=\"20150608183707671\" width=\"550\" height=\"501\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608183707671.png 583w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608183707671-300x273.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-395133\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608180313505.jpg\" alt=\"20150608180313505\" width=\"550\" height=\"486\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608180313505.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608180313505-300x265.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608180256352.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-395132\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608180256352.jpg\" alt=\"20150608180256352\" width=\"440\" height=\"440\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608180256352.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608180256352-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608180256352-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608180256352-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/20150608180256352-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@苏菲的星星：这几天不停看到无知的人义愤填膺地站出来给AWW洗地有点受不了。先说，我并不觉得佩佩反华，但他说自己是aww的longtime fan确实不妥当。其次，aww地精们很明显没搞清楚你们跪舔了怎样一个人。他fuck中国的那些事已经人尽皆知，除此之外，偷税漏税，重婚，让老婆做鸡，卖十二生肖铜像，详细看图好吗？</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-395121 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e8%89%be%e6%9c%aa%e6%9c%aa%e6%ac%ba%e4%b8%96%e7%9b%97%e5%90%8d-%e8%ae%be%e8%ae%a1%e8%b0%8b%e5%ae%b3%e9%a1%be%e5%9f%8e%e3%80%81%e6%b5%b7%e5%ad%90/cb069b10jw1eswh4g5difj20hs0vkafx/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/cb069b10jw1eswh4g5difj20hs0vkafx-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/cb069b10jw1eswh4g5difj20hs0vkafx-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/cb069b10jw1eswh4g5difj20hs0vkafx-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/cb069b10jw1eswh4g5difj20hs0vkafx-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e8%89%be%e6%9c%aa%e6%9c%aa%e6%ac%ba%e4%b8%96%e7%9b%97%e5%90%8d-%e8%ae%be%e8%ae%a1%e8%b0%8b%e5%a